---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import TeamsCTA from "../components/cta/TeamsCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="People - ROM Business Psychology">

<!-- HERO SECTION -->
<section class="relative min-h-[50vh] flex items-center pt-20 overflow-hidden">
  <img 
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1449824913935-59a10b8d2000?w=1920&h=800&fit=crop" 
    alt="City at night"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover scale-110"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-900/80 backdrop-blur-sm"></div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl py-20">
      <h2 class="text-white leading-relaxed text-left">
        In a constantly changing world, if you donâ€™t develop, 
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-cyan-500/20 border-l-4 border-cyan-400 font-bold my-2">
          you fall behind.
        </span>
       
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SHARPENING THE HUMAN FACTOR -->
<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mb-4 font-semibold">
      People
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-gray-900 mb-8 leading-tight">
          Sharpening the Human Factor
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none p-4 shadow-sm ml-auto max-w-sm">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-1">
            CFO: "What if we invest in developing our people, and then they leave?"
          </p>
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">21:36</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-green-100 border border-green-200 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none p-4 shadow-sm mr-auto max-w-sm">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-800 mb-1">
            CEO: "What if we don't, and they stay?!"
          </p>
          <span class="text-xs text-green-600 flex items-center gap-1 justify-end">
            21:36
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-12">
      <p class="font-semibold">People crave personal and professional development.</p>
      <p>Creating harmonious spaces for people to reach their full potential is the most valuable managerial effort leaders ought to be engaged in.</p>
      <p>However, sometimes leaders are not qualified enough for this important mission.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTEXT & CHALLENGE SECTION -->
<section class="bg-white py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      
      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-teal-500 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 blur transition duration-500"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 mb-6 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 shadow-lg transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-gray-900 mb-4 group-hover:text-cyan-600 transition-colors">
            The context
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
            It's an hectic reality. Everyday millions of new webpages are added, new discoveries, novel approaches. In these days individuals acknowledge the fact 'I'm the product' - I ought to continuously develop myself.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-500 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 blur transition duration-500"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 mb-6 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 shadow-lg transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-gray-900 mb-4 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
            The challenge
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
            In order to cope with the multitude of day-to-day challenges, people are required to sharpen their behavioral skills, enhance self awareness and improve their ability to interact effectively. Human development is a continuous journey. It involves designing and redesigning our knowledge, perceptions, emotions, and beliefs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>



<!-- Broadening Personal Capacity Section -->

<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      
      <!-- Left Column - Text -->
      <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
        <p class="text-cyan-600 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
          Our value proposition
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Broadening personal capacity
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Through personal consultation, individuals can explore their inner world and assess its compatibility to their current as well as future challenges. Nonetheless, merely enhancing self-awareness is not enough; the developmental process also involves learning and assimilating new mental templates, behavioral patterns, habits and routines.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          This is where we come along by offering 3 solutions for enhancing personal growth, capacity, and performance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column - Cards -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        
        <!-- Executive Coaching -->
        <a href="/executive-coaching" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-12 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 block" style="background-color: #1e3a8a;">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10 group-hover:bg-black/0 transition-colors"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-white card-title mb-4 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
              Executive Coaching
            </h3>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
              "For the last few weeks I've been struggling with a dilemma regarding my team..."
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center text-white font-medium">
              Learn more
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ms-2 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Career Development -->
        <a href="/career-development" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-12 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 block" style="background-color: #1e3a8a;">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10 group-hover:bg-black/0 transition-colors"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-white card-title mb-4 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
              Career Development
            </h3>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
              "I'm not sure if this is the right job for me..."
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center text-white font-medium">
              Learn more
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ms-2 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Emotional Therapy -->
        <a href="/emotional-therapy" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-12 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 block" style="background-color: #1e3a8a;">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10 group-hover:bg-black/0 transition-colors"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-white card-title mb-4 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
              Emotional Therapy
            </h3>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
              "No matter what I do or how many achievements I accomplish, it just doesn't feel right."
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center text-white font-medium">
              Learn more
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ms-2 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<TeamsCTA />
<Footer />
</Layout>